<p id="solar-experience" style="font-size: 1.2em; font-weight: bold;">Solar Project Design Experience at HCB Solar</p><br><ul style="list-style-type: none;">    <li><strong>Project Types:</strong>        <ul>            <li>Designed over 100 residential solar projects.</li>            <li>Specialized in both off-grid and on-grid systems.</li>            <li>Expertise in systems with and without batteries, including AC and DC coupling.</li>            <li>Worked with leading brands like Enphase, Tesla, and Sonnen.</li>        </ul>    </li>    <br>    <li><strong>Inverter Knowledge:</strong>        <ul>            <li>Utilized a variety of inverters including:</li>            <li>Micro-inverters (Enphase)</li>            <li>Inverters with optimizers (SolarEdge)</li>            <li>String-inverters (SMA, Fronius)</li>        </ul>    </li>    <br>    <li><strong>Design and Compliance:</strong>        <ul>            <li>Created designs based on site photos and satellite imagery.</li>            <li>Ensured compliance with standards for battery placement.</li>        </ul>    </li>    <br>    <li><strong>Documentation and Approval:</strong>        <ul>            <li>Produced Single Line Diagrams (SLD) for each system.</li>            <li>Managed grid connection applications with distributors like Ausgrid and Essential Energy.</li>        </ul>    </li>    <br>    <li><strong>Installation Coordination:</strong>        <ul>            <li>Collaborated with on-site teams to facilitate smooth installation processes.</li>        </ul>    </li></ul>